@NODE WI_MAINWIN "Main window"

This is the main window of Photoalbum Creator II.
It consists of:
@{" The main window    " link WI_MAINWIN }
@{" The options window " link WI_OPTSWIN }
@{" The preview window " link WI_PREVWIN }
@{" The menustrip      " link WI_MENU    }
@{" The toolbar        " link WI_TOOLBAR }
