@ENDNODE

@NODE WI_OPTSWIN "The options window"

        The toolbar gives you quick access to some of the most commonly
        used functions of the menu.
        
@ENDNODE

@NODE WI_OPTSWIN "The options window"

Toolbar options
- Appearance: Choose if you want text, images or both in the buttons of the toolbar.
- Label position: Choose where you want the text of the buttons.
- Bar position: Choose the alignment of the buttons in the bar.
- General appearance of the toolbar: Just experiment with these options, there's something in there for everyone...

Generation options
- Color scheme
- Layout style
- Border for images
- Cleanup before generating

Startup options
Default project

Option buttons
- Cancel
- Apply options
- Save options
        
@ENDNODE

@NODE WI_PREVWIN "The preview window"

Nothing much to say here really.
This is just a quick preview window to quickly check the appearance of the page you just made. 
This saves you the trouble of starting a seperate browser.
But keep in mind that this might look quite different from within a browser.
        
@ENDNODE

@NODE WI_MENU "The menustrip"

File - New
File - Open
File - Save
File - Save as
File - Generate photoalbum
File - Quit

Edit - Insert
