View - HTML
View - Options

Help - Contents
Help - About MUI
Help - About Photoalbum Creator II
        
@ENDNODE

@NODE WI_TOOLBAR "The toolbar"

The toolbar gives you quick access to some of the most commonly used functions of the menu.
Most menu options are also available in the toolbar.
        
@ENDNODE

@NODE WI_MSGAREA "The messagearea"

The message area will inform you with notes, warnings or errors.
        
@ENDNODE



